  "texts": [
    "It should be noted that due to the increasing number of publications, the following analysis results can only reflect the latest research status as of the retrieval date.Based on the number of papers published (as shown in Fig. 2), there has been a surge in the number of articles related to the application of AI in tribology since 2016.",
    "In just five years, the annual publication volume has increased by about 20 times, with 506 papers published in 2022 alone.",
    "This coincides with the year when AlphaGo defeated the world chess champion (2016) [20].",
    "There is no doubt that this global event not only sparked a revolution in the computer field, but also brought new ideas and methods to solve problems in many other fields [21].",
    "From the perspective of journal publication volume, the distribution of publications is extremely scattered, and the journal International Journal of Advanced Manufacturing Technology with the highest proportion of publications is only 4.89%."
  ]
}